1. Graphic session: <username> and hit enter
	1.1: <password> and hit enter

2. Using ssh connection from terminal:
	2.1: su <password> (in your debian VM)
	2.2: apt-get install openssh-server
	2.3: systemctl ssh status
		 2.3.1: if it's not running the run <systemctl start ssh>
	3.0: connect to the VM from your terminal using 'ssh <username>@<IP address>'
		 example: ssh pskytta@10.11.199.42
